title: Former British Ambassador Says He, Not Russia, Is the DNC Leak
subtitle: Craig Murray, described as a "close associate" of WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange, claims the leaks of DNC e-mails came from the inside.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Leaks of DNC e-mails were  stemmed from the efforts of a disgruntled insider, not Russian hackers.
